# Project Context

## Overview
This project uses the Ralph Loop pattern. Each agent instance works on exactly one task
from tasks.json, then exits. A new agent is spawned with fresh context.

## Conventions
- Tasks are in tasks.json. Work on the FIRST task where `passes: false` (and not blocked/skipped).
- Mark completion by setting `passes: true` in tasks.json (do not change other fields).
- Log what you did and any learnings to progress.txt after each task.
- Commit after each successful task.

